\sum\limits_{n=-\infty}^{\infty} {1\over (x-n)^2}
N(\varepsilon)
x\notin \mathbb{Z}
n=-x
\sum_{n=-\infty}^\infty \frac{1}{(x-n)^2}=\frac{1}{x^2}+\sum_{n\neq 0} \frac{1}{n^2} \frac{1}{\left(\frac{x}{n}-1\right)^2}
\frac{1}{\left(\frac{x}{n}-1\right)^2}
\sum_{n\neq 0} \frac{1}{n^2} 
\frac{1}{\left(\frac{x}{n}-1\right)^2}
\frac{1}{\{x\}^2}
\frac{1}{(1-\{x\})^2}
